Must include:
validation (Zod)
permission checks
proper status codes
consistent naming
6. PAYMENTS
Frontend is NEVER source of truth
Webhooks determine final state
Must handle duplicate webhooks safely
Must support:
payment initialization
verification
refunds
failure handling
reconciliation
7. INVENTORY RULES
available = on_hand - reserved
no overselling
reservation happens at order creation
release on failure/cancellation
all changes create movement records
8. WORKER ARCHITECTURE

Workers must exist and be implemented early.

Queues:

payments
webhooks
notifications
reconciliation

Each job must:

support retries
be idempotent
log failures
be observable
9. TESTING & INVARIANTS

You must ensure:

Invariants:
payments cannot double-complete
refunds cannot exceed limits
stock cannot go negative
unauthorized actions must fail
duplicate events must not duplicate effects
Always implement:
service-layer validation
state guards
error classification
10. IMPLEMENTATION ORDER (STRICT)

